Description: Tools for importing, processing, and exporting Swiss inpatient hospital data
    (SpiGes) in various formats. Supports XML and CSV import, as well as export
    to XML, SwissDRG, and SPLG formats. Handles multilingual code lists and
    variable conversion according to the SpiGes documentation.
